haizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">当别人给了你什么东西之后，<br>他们就会期望得到回报，<br>如果你不给他们回报，<br>他们就再也不会给予你什么了。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《掌控谈话》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第7章，第149页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">达成协议的艺术，<br>要坚持聚焦到最后。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《掌控谈话》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第8章，第184页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">应聘者提出一个薪酬期望的范围，<br>比只提出一个具体数字往往能得到更高的薪酬结果。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《掌控谈话》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第6章，第131页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">过于急躁是所有谈判者都容易犯的错误之一，<br>任由时间流逝是谈判者能使用的最重要的手段之一。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《掌控谈话》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第2章，第30页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  let flipSwitchTimer = null\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', event => {\n    if (event.target.closest('a')) return\n    const card = event.target.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail .zhaizhai-flip-card')\n    if (!card) return\n    if (flipSwitchTimer) {\n      clearTimeout(flipSwitchTimer)\n      flipSwitchTimer = null\n    }\n    const container = card.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail')\n    const cards = container ? container.querySelectorAll('.zhaizhai-flip-card.is-flipped') : []\n    const isFlipped = card.classList.contains('is-flipped')\n\n    cards.forEach(item => {\n      if (item !== card) item.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    })\n\n    if (isFlipped) {\n      card.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    } else {\n      const hasOtherFlipped = [...cards].some(item => item !== card)\n      if (hasOtherFlipped) {\n        // Close previous card first, then open target card for smoother switch.\n        flipSwitchTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n          card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n          flipSwitchTimer = null\n        }, 120)\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n      }\n    }\n  })\n})()\n</script>\n</body></html>","raw":"---\ntitle: 掌控谈话\ndate: 2026-04-07 06:20:54\ntype: page\naside: true\ncomments: false\n---\n\n> 共 14 条摘录，最近更新：2026-03-27\n\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-冷静\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">谈判</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2024-10-30</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">“不”是谈判的开始，<br>而不是结束。<br>“不”常常是一个决定，<br>往往是临时性的，<br>目的是保持谈判现状。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《掌控谈话》</d